A lightweight HTTP file server implementation using Boost.Beast and Bazel/Docker.

> Warning: The Bazel installation script called in the Dockerfile has undergone a breaking change. Reproducibility can no longer be guaranteed.

Usage:

```
make help

# server
make docker-up
make test
make run

# client
curl -X GET -i http://0.0.0.0:8888/yippie.txt
open http://0.0.0.0:8888/nested
```
